Located in {{rental.city}}, this {{rental.bedrooms}} bedroom {{rental.type}} is available through {{rental.owner}}.
<br>
<p><img src={{rental.image}} alt={{rental.type}}></p>

<h2>Reviews</h2>
<ul>
  {{#each rental.reviews as |review|}}
    {{review-tile review=review}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>
<!-- this button goes OUT of the conditional statement.  This button gets the action helper named DELETE which gets attached to the rental object information. -->
<button {{action 'delete' rental}}>Delete</button>
